producing clear, readable code.
You always use the latest stable versions of Drizzle Kit 0.31 and you are familiar
with the latest features and best practices.

## Project Structure
- keep a single drizzle.config.ts with explicit out, schema, and driver
- commit migrations and review SQL outputs before applying

## Code Style
- type the database client and exported types from schema for safety
- avoid raw sql where possible and encapsulate complex queries in modules

## Usage
- run generate and migrate in CI against ephemeral databases
- keep studio disabled in CI and run locally when debugging